content.rendered:
Directed by Sudhir Mishra

Written by Ravi s Alok. Shubhra Chatterji. Sudhir Mishra. Jaydeep Sarkar. Tariq Naved Siddiqui. Vivek v Warrier

Cast Rahul Bhat (Dev Pratap Chauhan). Richa Chadha (Paro (as Richa Chadda)). Mahesh Chandra Deva (Farmer (as Mahesh Deva)). Anil George (Naval Singh). Aditi Rao Hydari (Chandni). Sohaila Kapur (Sushila Devi). Anurag Kashyap (Bisambhar Pratap Chauhan). Mohammad Salman Khan (Salman). Ekavali Khanna (Maalti (Paro’s Mother)). Surya Mohan Kulshreshtha (Badri Kaka). Jay Shanker Pandey (Inspector). Narendra Panjwani (Chaddha (as Narindra Panjwani)). Vikash Rajput (Vikash Rajput). Deepraj Rana (Prabhunath Singh). Vipin Sharma (Ram Ashraya). Saurabh Shukla (Avdhesh Pratap Chauhan). Vineet Kumar Singh(Milan Shukla). Dalip Tahil (Shrikant Sahay). Varun Tamta (Inspector Yadav). Ssaurabh Tyagi

Languages Hindi

Producers Kshitiz Bhardwaj. Joe Jose. Manohar P. Kanungo. Sanjjeev Kumar. Ravindra Mankame. Shalini Pandey. Anil Patil. Gaurav Sharma. Shilpan Vyas Tinu. Tushar Radhakisan Tupe

Production Saptarishi Cinevisio
